Online Ordering System

* HTML form submission
* HTML table layouts
* PHP web form processing
* PHP using Classes
* PHP XML file reading

The System
An order system where the menu items come from an XML file

1. Input page
 - HTML form using arrays to capture data
 - reads XML
 - uses a PHP Class to manage the XML data file
 - uses food item title and costs to display for ordering


2. Output page
 - reads XML
 - uses XML data to get item costs to calculate order and output order for confirmation
 - uses a PHP Class to manage the XML data file
 